"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/56/1922/abstract/7\">",
"      Simpson DP, Hager SR. Bicarbonate-carbon dioxide buffer system: a determinant of the mitochondrial pH gradient. Am J Physiol 1984; 247:F440.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
