"      Endoscopic ultrasound: Normal pancreaticobiliary anatomy",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?27/13/27866?source=related_link\">",
"      Epidemiology and risk factors for exocrine pancreatic cancer",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?32/37/33370?source=related_link\">",
"      Management of locally advanced and borderline resectable exocrine pancreatic cancer",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
